MID_支援_カゲロウ_リョウマ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$Wmリョウマ|3$w0|$Wsリョウマ|$WaKagerou, do you have some time?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaAh, Lord Ryouma.\nWhat do you need of me?$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|Oh, nothing. I don't require anything.\nJust the opposite, actually.$k$pI'm rarely able to show my gratitude to you,\nso, is there anything you would like?\n$k$p If there is anything you desire,\nI'd like to hear it.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|!!\nThose words are too good for me...!$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|No...I'm not speaking of anything so grand.\n$k$pFor all the times you've cared for me,\nI want to return the favor.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|I'm indebted to you, Lord Ryouma...!$k$pBut, I never expected you would ask\nsomething like this of me...$k$pIt's difficult...$k$pHmm...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|You don't have to think too seriously.$k$pIf there is something unusual you would\nlike to eat, or wear, anything like that.\n$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,汗|But...I'm a bit embarrased.\nI've not thought about these matters...$k$pFor me, serving you is an honor.\n$k$pThat is more than enough...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|...Is there really nothing?$k$p…………$k$p$E笑,|Well then, Kagerou, this is an order.\nThink of something you want to do.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|Wh-what...?!$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$WaThink well, as I'll ask you about\n this every time we meet.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|Th-that's...ugh.\nMy head aches...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|That's because you're thinking too hard.\nI want to hear your honest wishes.$k$pWell then, I look forward to it.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wd$w0|$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|Ah, he left...!$k$pWhat...what will I do?$k
MID_支援_カゲロウ_リョウマ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$Wmリョウマ|3$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|Lord Ryouma...$k$pThe other day, you asked me\nto think of a request for you...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$WaAh, that matter?\nAnd what of it?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaSince then, I've continued to think.\nI really thought hard about it...$k$pSo...there is truly only one\nthing I can request of you.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|Oh, what is it?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|I...would like to train with you,\nLord Ryouma.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E怒,|Train with me?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|From the beginning, I've wanted to match\nyour skill in swordsmanship, so I trained.$k$pBut, if I were to experience your strength\nfirst-hand, I think I could surely improve.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|I see...\nHeh, that sounds like you, Kagerou.$k$pI'm glad that you've\ntold me what you want.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Lord Ryouma...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|Above all, being asked to train\na subordinate is a sign of trust.$k$pAs such, I will accept your request.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|Then, you will be my opponent?$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Aah, of course.\nIf that is your wish, then I shall oppose you.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Lord Ryouma...truly, thank you.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|Haha, aren't you too quick to give thanks?$k$pYou've asked me rather suddenly,\nafter all.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Huh...I suppose so.\nThen, I will face you with all my strength!$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes. I'll be a serious opponent as well.\nLet's go, Kagerou!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|Yes, sir!$k
MID_支援_カゲロウ_リョウマ_Ａ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$Wmリョウマ|3$w0|$Wsリョウマ|$WaKagerou.\nHow was our duel the other day?$k$pAre you content with it?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaWhen you showed me your true skill\nwith a sword, I had several thoughts...$k$pTruly, there was much I didn't know\nbecause I was only by your side.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|That's good.$k$pHowever, I cannot accept\nthat as your sole request.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|That's...\nThat is already enough.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|I won't hear of it.$k$pHow would you feel about a tea ceremony?\nI'd be happy to join... What do you think?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|Tea...is it?$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|You like calm places, don't you, Kagerou?$k$pSo, let's have tea together,\nand relieve some of your fatigue...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|I'm sorry that you have to worry about\nthat, Lord Ryouma. I'm truly lucky...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E怒,|You're working yourself to death.\nIt's necessary to relax.$k$pHaving the drive to grow is important,\nbut it's meaningless if you don't rest.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|I'm understand, but pushing through\nhardship is part of my character...$k$pBut, since it is your advice, Lord Ryouma,\nI'll bear it in mind.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes.\nFrom now on, please take care of yourself.$k$pThis is my request for you.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|As you wish.\nI will do my best...!$k
MID_支援_カゲロウ_リョウマ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmカゲロウ|7$Wmリョウマ|3$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|Kagerou. You've been working non-stop\nrecently... Are you all right?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|Lord Ryouma, that...\nI'm glad for your concern, but...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E怒,|The other day, when we went out for tea,\nI brought it up, but you paid no attention...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|No...you're mistaken!$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|Then, why are you working so desperately?$k$pI'm glad that you're so devoted,\nbut I'm worried about you...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|That's...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|Is it something you can't tell your master?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|...!$k$pNo... It's because you are\nmy master that I can't say it...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E怒,|What do you mean?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,照汗|I... I've been harboring unforgivable\nfeelings towards you...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,|What...?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|I've always respected you\nfrom the very beginning.$k$pBut...whenever I was experiencing troubles,\nyou moved me with your kindness.$k$p$E笑,|So then, I began to feel something\nother than just a sense of duty...$k$pSome strange feeling...\nAfter that, I spoke with a close friend.$k$pAnd then...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E怒,|What did they say?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,照汗|That...\nThat I was in love.$k$pI...\nI am in love with you, Lord Ryouma.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E通常,汗|Kagerou...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,照汗|Of course, I know my position.\nI could never marry you...$k$pBut to continue to support you at the side,\nthe pain of being close to you...$k$pIt tormented my heart.$k$p$Eキメ,照汗|So that's why I falsely took a\nday off and returned to working...$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|So that was it...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|But, beyond revealing my feelings\nfor you, none of what I've said matters.$k$pIf it is the case that I am a brother to you,\nthen I intened to resign as your retainer.$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|W-wait!\nWho said anything about being a brother?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|Lord Ryouma...?$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E苦,|That I didn't understand your\ntrue feelings is inexcusable.$k$pSo, from now on...please swear that\nyou won't say painful things like that.$k$p$Eキメ,照|Kagerou...I also love you.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,照|Lord Ryouma...!$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,照|After you finished speaking earlier,\nI didn't think...$k$pI was also touched by your kindness,\nand I always felt at ease with you.$k$pBut, for a lord to feel that way\nwas unthinkable, so I was lost...$k$p$E苦,照|And at that time, the one most important\nto me was hurting... What a pathetic tale.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,照|Lord Ryouma...\nThose words, do you really mean them?$k\n$Wsリョウマ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes. From now on, we are no longer master\nand servant, but together as one.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,照|...Thank you for your words.$k$pI...will always be by your side...!$k
